   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "We can start with some values for an initial not-so-accurate regression line, $y = .6x + 133.33$."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
